TopicTitle: Six girls went to a party in the mountains in their ol' 1960's pickup

Articles.Content:
Gilina, Patrid, Lizly, Micie, Versei and Rosrys wanted to go old style in Patrid her 1962 pickup she had just finished restoring, and make a huge impression at Bill's party. It was a succes, the guys drooled and other girls were jealous. Jeb wanted to drive it but the girls stood between him and the car. Very comfy ride due to complex suspension. Give it a try!
